<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link
    href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Nunito+Sans:opsz,wght@6..12,300&family=Source+Serif+4:opsz@8..60&display=swap"
    rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Nunito Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 400;
      text-align: center;
      color: #000000;
    }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Source Serif 4', serif;
      font-size: 900;
      color: #f25d27;
      font-size: 2.5em;
      margin-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .footer-text {
      font-size: 300;
      color: #777777;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    a {
      color: #f25d27;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <h1>
    <% if File.file? "#{Rails.root.join(" app", "assets" , "images" )}/logo.png" %>
      <%= image_tag "logo.png", width: "40" %>
    <% end %>
    <span>Silva Numerica</span>
  </h1>

  <%= yield %>

  <p class="footer-text"><a href="https://silva-numerica-oauth.fondation-unit.fr/">Silva Numerica</a>
    <br />
    Pour ne plus recevoir de notifications par email,<br />désactivez la fonctionnalité
    <a href="https://silva-numerica-oauth.fondation-unit.fr/settings">dans votre profil</a>.
  </p>
</body>
</html>